# Reaper image (Dockerfile.reaper) only needs the prebuilt binary in dist/.
# Exclude everything else so the build context stays small.
*
# Re-include every per-arch reaper binary: prod builds amd64, the local KIND
# local dev (dev-image) cross-builds the host arch (arm64 on Colima). Dockerfile.reaper
# COPYs dist/sandbox-linux-${TARGETARCH}.
!dist/sandbox-linux-*
